                           Ruby/SplitWhere
                           ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


0. INTRODUCTION
1. REQUIREMENTS
2. INSTALLATION
3. LICENSE
4. AUTHOR


0. INTRODUCTION
===============

split_where is the best split for specific situations, such as when a character is within quotation marks or apostrophes, use your imagination.


1. REQUIREMENTS
===============

Ruby/SplitWhere requires Ruby version 1.8.7 or newer.


2. INSTALLATION
===============

gem install split-where


